info.description: Front End Engineer with exposure to both small and large scale web application development. Experience collaborating with other developers, product managers, and design teams. Currently on the Site Development team at Walt Disney Direct-to-Consumer & International, where I work on front end projects across Disney's brands using Node, React, and MobX.
